{"tid":315804,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[求教]已經飲奶粉兩個月，體重沒有改善","createTime":"2017-07-10T09:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T14:07:03.000Z","uid":71398,"like":11,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"beab64dace51d1cc48ebab7d858ea68cb8d79c34","tid":315804,"uid":71398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T09:37:33.000Z","msg":"因為夏天想變大隻，所以由五月開始飲奶粉 做體能<br />\n每日飲一杯奶 + 每日做30下掌上壓(分2組做)，狀態好會做40下，每個星期六仲會做多20下SET UP<br />\n已經KEEP左成2個月，唔知係咪天生基因問題，體重都仲係得110kg 無重過，有無健身既師兄指教下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps: 16歲仔，間唔中同d同學會踢下波<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/173430_2533b602a36f9dce6d377aecbe46f2bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F173430_2533b602a36f9dce6d377aecbe46f2bf.jpg&h=48ca26db&s={SIZE}\" /> 依家個身型無明顯改進<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.hktvmall.com/h0888001/a644b950728111e4ad5eefb39c1508a589c63a36/h0888001_10021938_160928115404_01_300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.hktvmall.com%2Fh0888001%2Fa644b950728111e4ad5eefb39c1508a589c63a36%2Fh0888001_10021938_160928115404_01_300.jpg&h=179c24d7&s={SIZE}\" /> 飲緊呢隻奶粉，唔知好唔好<br />\n<br />\n希望體育台既師兄比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3b16fe1e7141e66146d20d6901b08eddbbe9e7","tid":315804,"uid":35653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"做太多啦<br />\n專家建議每星期30下就夠<br />\n你咁樣係唔會大隻"},{"pid":"bdd416d538a2a15edba7db1bb8f31e3a95851965","tid":315804,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T09:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做太多啦<br />\n專家建議每星期30下就夠<br />\n你咁樣係唔會大隻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n30下？<br />\n你想佢變Hulk呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3717bf78d89e58c3fb697d439be407906ae2bcd7","tid":315804,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2